362
00:28:04,170 --> 00:28:07,020
Madam, you'll become an administrative consultant at least.

363
00:28:07,020 --> 00:28:08,490
Come in.

364
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:10,700
- We'll be going in first.
- Please come in.
- Madam Liu, please.

365
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:13,700
