483
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,400
<i>Give us a kiss!</i>

484
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,000
- Great!
<i>- Give us a kiss!</i>

485
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,600
Give us a kiss!

